{"tid":2294614,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"掃4伙柏傲莊I！買家感幸運：相信因自己經常行善","createTime":"2020-11-21T07:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T14:55:58.000Z","uid":31798,"like":6,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aae4afcfb9e60cf1804da679a57214addfb1253f","tid":2294614,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"新世界發展(017)與港鐵(066)合作發展的大圍站上蓋項目柏傲莊I首輪及次輪銷售均沽清所有可售單位， 中原地產於項目創下銷售佳績，其中元朗峻巒分行客戶陳先生，成功於柏傲莊I次輪銷售大手購入4伙三房單位，斥資約6,700萬元，計劃作投資用途。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生稱，心儀柏傲莊坐落於沙中綫，覺得價錢吸引，等候項目開售已久，對成功大手入市感到十分幸運及開心，相信因為自己經常行善，本身在香港經營口罩生產業務，新冠肺炎疫情間已捐出超過100萬個口罩予慈善機構、學校、老人院等，與港人疫境同行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來只要做善事就買到柏傲莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af0932f297ad9d4cb4d0496530c5140f528e0c1","tid":2294614,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"撻定都要感謝神"},{"pid":"f368081ce92e6b344db0b69e2513a776d48084c2","tid":2294614,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做AA咁有錢"},{"pid":"f8e4a8d84643a84c7d0c70867bd81c68e9f9d6ee","tid":2294614,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"同佢開單AA有冇行善？"},{"pid":"7bff4418824186568dd0836073147b94726d1166","tid":2294614,"uid":22839,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f8e4a8d84643a84c7d0c70867bd81c68e9f9d6ee","tid":2294614,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"同佢開單AA有冇行善？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"有開單AA = 行善<br />\n無開單AA = 行乞"},{"pid":"9d23113faa80a865b6e9a4d4ba184e550f892e